    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3463" key="#Princeps">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Longobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/3664">Tassilonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> nostri, tibi <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Slave"
                                ><name ref="Walpertus">Waldiperto</name> fideli nostro filius <name
                                ref="Grasulfus">Grasulfi</name> hos <rs key="#Slave">servos</rs>
                            <rs key="#Palatium">sacri nostri palatii</rs>, <name ref="Ursibertus"
                                >Ursipertus</name>
                            <rs key="#Conductores">conductorem</rs>, <name ref="Leopardus"
                                >Leopardum</name> et <name ref="Leo">Leone</name>, <name ref="Ursus"
                                >Ursus</name>, <name ref="Lupus">Lupus</name> nec non et <name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name>, <name ref="Trasmundus"
                                >Trasemundus</name>, <name ref="Carolus">Carulu</name>, <name
                                ref="Bonellus">Bonellu</name>, alio <name ref="Leo">Leone</name>,
                                <name ref="Ermerisci">Ermerissi</name>, <name ref="Iordanus"
                                >Iordanne</name>, <name ref="Lupus">Lupu</name> et <name
                                ref="Palumbus">Palumbu</name> seu <name ref="Roppulus"
                                >Roppulus</name>, is autem omnibus cum uxoribus, filiis, filiabus,
                            nuris hac nepotibus et cum cispitibus et omnibus eorum
                        pertinentiis</rs>, et esse videtur conmorantes ex loco Parcorano ex finibus
                        Cimitiro, pertinunt de <placeName ref="#places/2354"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Actio #Slave">acto
                            Caudense</placeName>, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per
                        hęc nostrum roboreum preceptum predicta omnia que superius legitur tu et
                        heredes tui habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus,
                        id est comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptus
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego<persName
                            ref="#people/3465" key="#Notary">Audoaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> primo anno, mense octuber,
                        tertia indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
